Package: nngeo
Type: Package
Title: k-Nearest Neighbor Join for Spatial Data
Version: 0.1.5
Authors@R: c(
    person("Michael", "Dorman", email = "dorman@post.bgu.ac.il", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Jan", "Antala", email = "hello@janantala.com", role = c("ctb")))
Description: K-nearest neighbor search for projected and non-projected 'sf' spatial layers. Nearest neighbor search uses (1) C implementation of the Vicenty Formula for lon-lat point data, (2) function nn2() from package 'RANN' for projected point data, or (3) function st_distance() from package 'sf' for other types of spatial data.
Imports:
    geosphere,
    RANN,
    units,
    lwgeom,
    Rcpp
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.3),
    sf (>= 0.6-0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
BugReports: https://github.com/michaeldorman/nngeo/issues
LinkingTo: Rcpp
